<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb52be270-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s492"><num value="492">§ 492.</num><heading> Function</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The function of the Council shall be to advise the President on homeland security matters.</p>
